data.description: Looking for a home with room and room to grow, well here it is. This home offers 4 bedrooms plus a bonus room. It has a separate DR and Living and there's also a hearth room off the kitchen with a fireplace.  2 bedrooms up and 2 bedrooms down. The seller has added new hardwood upstair and upgraded the flooring and bathrooms. There a detached garage with plenty of storage space and a small building behind it for more storage or was used as a upscale dog house with heat & ac. A must see.
